Requirements:
=============

Mandatory:

C compiler

Optional:

pkg-config
gtk+-2.0 + gdk-pixbuf + development files


Building:
=========

One-time build:
    ./build.sh

To build without the GTK+-2.0 GUI, type:
    ./build.sh cli

Clean up:
    ./build.sh clean

Cleaner up:
    ./build.sh distclean

Just configure:
    ./build.sh configure

Et cetera. For all build actions and options like --cc and --prefix:
    ./build.sh --help
